"{\"uid\": \"eonline.com-news-1405876-2024-olympics-gymnast-ana-barbosu-taking-social-media-break-after-scoring-controversy\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Romania's Ana Barbosu announced she's taking a step back from social media after she missed out on bronze at the 2024 Paris Olympics to Jordan Chiles following a score inquiry.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6928094877976856, \"rank\": 0.44228299452494696, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GymnastAna Barbosuis heading offline.\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the Romanian gymnast found herself at the center of attention at the 2024 Paris Olympics after achange to the final scoreof Team USA'sJordan Chiles' floor eventbumped her off the winner's podium, she announced she's pressing mute on the noise.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9997905193716431, \"rank\": 0.00017689455371349536, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9085518332709651, \"rank\": 0.0764878672156569, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you everyone for the support messages!\\\"\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ana wrote in English on herAugust 7 Instagram Storyover a photo of the Olympic rings in Paris at sunset, \\\"I will take a break from the social media.\\\"\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.1560703184362946e-24, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999343913281, \"rank\": 6.56086783693919e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added in Romanian, alongside a smiling emoji, \\\"For those who know me, you have my number.\\\"\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9997905193716431, \"rank\": 0.00017689455371349536, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the second time the 18-year-old hasshared a social media messagefollowing her medal loss, the first echoing her feelings of gratitude.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you to everyone who encouraged me,\\\" she wrote Aug. 5, \\\"before, during, and after the competition.\\\"\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time, she also reposted a Story from retired Romanian gymnastSandra Izbasa-Biancacheering her on.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9997905193716431, \"rank\": 0.00017689455371349536, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hear more vividly than ever the words that the coaches repeated to us almost daily in the training room,\\\" Sandra wrote in Romanian.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Reemer\", \"score\": 0.8441252245272208, \"rank\": 0.1846512365831759, \"text\": \"Sandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Reemer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Reemer\"}, {\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9997905193716431, \"rank\": 0.00017689455371349536, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"'You, as Romanians, must be more than perfect in order not to leave room for interpretations!'\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\", \"score\": 0.9953616234783742, \"rank\": 0.003795621629716871, \"text\": \"Romanians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And here, it proves itself once again!\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Girls, head up and back straight!\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keep believing in your dreams!\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Go Romania!\\\"\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6928094877976856, \"rank\": 0.44228299452494696, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gymnastics individual final events on August 5, ended in a dramatic fashion after a last-minute inquiry into Jordan'sfloor score resulted in a 0.1 addition.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In this case, Jordan's team felt she executed a tour jet\\u00e9 with a full turn better than the judges marked her-they'd scored her a 5.8 in difficulty rather than the hoped-for 5.9.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9743599826619553, \"rank\": 0.025675769688062657, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But while coaches can not appeal execution scores, they can appeal difficulty ratings, and Jordan's coaches submitted an inquiry on her behalf-and the judges ultimately agreed.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9743599826619553, \"rank\": 0.025675769688062657, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The result not only changed Jordan's score from a 13.666 to a 13.766-it also changed the podium results.\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2014, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9743599826619553, \"rank\": 0.025675769688062657, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whereas Ana had thought she'd landed in the bronze position, behind fellow Team USA memberSimone BilesandBrazil'sRebeca Andrade, she suddenly found herself bumped to fourth place.\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9085518332709651, \"rank\": 0.0764878672156569, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2211, \"end\": 2218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999997088275874, \"rank\": 2.91047737123003e-07, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But while the result was understandably disappointing, asOlympic gymnastLaurie Hernandezshared during NBC's broadcast, \\\"That's why inquiries happen.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2374, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999065236799816, \"rank\": 8.561615588276815e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes, they do miss it, and they are able to go back and double check.\\\"\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking down into tears after seeing the adjusted scoreboard, Jordan later spoke to the emotional moment.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2561, \"end\": 2567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9743599826619553, \"rank\": 0.025675769688062657, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just wanted to come out and do the best I could,\\\" she told cameras following the medal ceremony.\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have no words-I am just very proud of myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your source for entertainment news, celebrities, celeb news, and \\u200bcelebrity gossip.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Check out the hottest fashion, photos, movies and TV shows!\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025E!\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Entertainment Television, LLC A Versant Media Company.\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2936, \"end\": 2939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999998833150198, \"rank\": 1.1668481932326981e-07, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"htt